<h2 style="color: #CCFF00; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -1px;">
  >> PASSWORD_RESET_REQUEST
</h2>

<p style="color: #E5E5E5; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
  TARGET_ID: <%= @resource.email %>
</p>

<p style="color: #A3A3A3; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
  A request to reset access credentials has been intercepted.
</p>

<div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
  <%= link_to '>> INITIATE_RESET_SEQUENCE', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "background-color: #CCFF00; color: #000000; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; display: inline-block;" %>
</div>

<p style="color: #666666; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #333333; padding-top: 10px;">
  SYSTEM_NOTE: If this request was not initiated by you, disregard this transmission. Credentials remain secure.
</p>
